article_id:262,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding the Void Battles Treasure Trade Menu Not Appearing [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have found an issue where, under certain conditions, the Void Battles Treasure Trade menu does not appear.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further updates will be added to this notice.<br><br><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550829600"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue was fixed on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550829600"></span><br>This issue can be resolved by restarting the game.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1550818800,update_time1550830262